query:
SELECT se.id, se.eventoId, se.formandoId, se.tipoServico, e.data as evento_data, e.tipoEvento
FROM servicos_execucao se
LEFT JOIN eventos e ON se.eventoId = e.id
WHERE se.formandoId = (SELECT id FROM formandos WHERE nome LIKE '%Ayna%' LIMIT 1)
